Description:
    Generates a migration to fetch data from a legacy database to this app.
    This also generate tests and fixtures from the actual data making possible
    to run both applications while you develop this and make sure that
    migrations will keep working.

Example:
    rails generate advancement:migration db/legacy/places.dbf

    Will create:
        app/advancement/places_migration.rb
        test/unit/advancement/places_migration_test.rb
        test/unit/advancement/fixtures/places.yml
